                <th style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 8px; text-align: left; background-color: #EBF8FF; font-weight: bold; color: #0D244F;">핵심 원리/목표</th>
                <th style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; padding: 8px; text-align: left; background-color: #EBF8FF; font-weight: bold; color: #0D244F;">ECR에서의 주요 강점</th>
